00:38:11,711 --> 00:38:13,275
<font color="#696969">I'm fine, sir.</font>

395
00:38:13,484 --> 00:38:14,735
<font color="#696969">Enjoying your classes?</font>

396
00:38:15,986 --> 00:38:19,010
<font color="#696969">I know Professor Slughorn
