507
00:48:26,033 --> 00:48:29,786
<font color="#696969">That's what it says right here: "This book is property of the Half-Blood Prince."</font>

508
00:48:47,094 --> 00:48:50,430
<font color="#696969">For weeks you carry around
this book, practically sleep with it....</font>

509
00:48:50,639 --> 00:48:52,933
<font color="#696969">....yet you have no desire to find out who he is?</font>

510
00:48:53,141 --> 00:48:56,478
<font color="#696969">I didn't say I wasn't curious, and I don't sleep with it.</font>

511
00:48:56,686 --> 00:48:57,729
<font color="#696969">Well, it's true.</font>

512
00:48:57,937 --> 00:49:01,691
<font color="#696969">I like a nice chat before I go to bed. Now all you do is read that bloody book.</font>

513
00:49:01,795 --> 00:49:03,776
<font color="#696969">It's just like being with Hermione.</font>

514
00:49:05,131 --> 00:49:07,634
<font color="#696969">Well, I was curious, so I went to....</font>

515
00:49:07,738 --> 00:49:10,345
<font color="#696969">~ The library.
