00:49:44,543 --> 00:49:45,794
<font color="#696969">Okay.</font>

527
00:49:47,254 --> 00:49:48,609
<font color="#696969">Something to drink?</font>

528
00:49:48,818 --> 00:49:51,320
<font color="#696969">Three Butterbeers,
