538
00:50:32,921 --> 00:50:34,902
<font color="#696969">And you, and you.</font>

539
00:50:35,111 --> 00:50:36,883
<font color="#696969">So, what brings you here?</font>

540
00:50:36,988 --> 00:50:41,784
<font color="#696969">The Three Broomsticks and I go way back, further than I care to admit.</font>

541
00:50:41,888 --> 00:50:45,329
