560
00:52:42,521 --> 00:52:47,317
<font color="#696969">Do not touch that, except by the wrappings. Do you understand?</font>

561
00:53:00,872 --> 00:53:03,374
<font color="#696969">You're sure Katie did not have this in her possession....</font>

562
00:53:03,582 --> 00:53:06,085
